snippet.title: #JobSeekerNation
snippet.description:
The purpose of #JobSeekerNation is to help job seekers and working professionals find work, pivot, change, and adapt to the modern job search challenges. 

Your hosts:

Jack Kelly and I (Mark Anthony Dyson) are the hosts. 

Jack is also a Senior Careers Contributor at Forbes. He writes several articles weekly to keep up with workplace, career, and job search trends. His career and job-search advice have been featured in Forbes, Inc., CNBC, Fox News, and many other outlets. He also hosts the WeCruiter podcast: Let's Go Live with Jack Kelly!

I (Mark) am the founder of the award-winning blog and podcast, The Voice of Job Seekers. I am always hacking and reimagining the modern job search to help you. I am the author and curator of the E-Book "421 Modern Job Search Tips 2021!

I've been featured in Forbes, Business Insider, Inc., Fast Company, and Linkedin News LIVE with Andrew Seaman, and many more.  

#jobsearch #jobseekers #JobSeekerNation
